<br>
5751 Stalwart Endurance<br>
5752 This ability grants a chance to endure what would otherwise be a stunning blow, from any angle, without being stunned.  You may train in this ability at or after levels 62 and 64.<br>
5753 You avoid the stunning blow.<br>
